<TEXT>
Hilton Hotels could record a net income increase of more than 20 per cent in
the fourth quarter ended December 31, despite taking a Dollars 12.5m
reserve, said Mr Raymond Avansino, president and chief operating officer,
AP-DJ reports from Beverly Hills.
