<HEADLINE>
FT  13 JAN 94 / UK Company News: Minstergate up
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pre-tax profit at Minstergate, the property manager and developer, was
Pounds 1.28m in the year to August 31, against Pounds 1.2m last time.
External sales shrank to Pounds 3.33m (Pounds 5.66m). Earnings leapt to
30.55p (0.72p) per share.
</TEXT>
