    TDZ  Chad, Africa.
    CFZ  Central African Republic, Africa.
    CGZ  Congo, Africa.
    FRZ  France, EC.
    KMZ  Comoros, Africa.
    MLZ  Mali, Africa.
    SNZ  Senegal, Africa.
    CIZ  Ivory Coast, Africa.
    BFZ  Burkina Faso, Africa.
